cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DC

This paper is primarily focused on the machine learning aspect of Federated Learning (FL) and proposes a new algorithm using Deep Reinforcement Learning (DRL) framework. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of network connection and training latency, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of DRL also indicates the possibility of it belonging to cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves predicting the qualities of training and reporting phases, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the metropolitan edge computing environment, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
